---
title: Creamy Beef & Pumpkin Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese & Chilli Flakes
description: There are plenty of choices for a good fusilli out there, but we’re positive we have the winning combination of ingredients that will top the lot. Savoury beef mince and sweet roasted pumpkin come together in a creamy sauce that clings to perfectly al dente fusilli. That sounds (and tastes) like the best to us.

*We’ve replaced the risoni in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
